A + Network shareholders approve merger . A + Network Inc said on Wednesday its shareholders approved the company ' s merger into Metrocall Inc . Holders of A + Network common stock at the effective time of the merger will have the right to receive 1 . 17877 shares of Metrocall stock , an equal number of variable common rights ( VCRs ) of Metrocall and cash in lieu of fractional shares and VCRs for each A + Network share . The merger transaction is expected to close by November 15 , the paging company said . 
